"O.  My first time having a Sahti and I gotta say I like it.  It's a nice change of pace from the IPA's and Stout's that I love so much.  This is a nice chill beer.  I think it would be great with a Ceasar salad or an olive oil based pasta dish.  Speaking of salad would probably make a great vinaigrette.   This is a nice delve into the style and I will look for more."
